{
  "texts": [
    "Hernandez-Bocanegra and Ziegler (2023) propose a dialogue system to explain hotel recommendations.",
    "Healthcare and smart home Shaheen et al. (2020) propose treatment plans for multicondition patients.",
    "Their solution involves a Satisfiability Modulo Theories (SMT) Solver (Moura and Bjørner 2011) to recommend optimal treatment paths, coupled with explainable dialogues to explain the suggestions.",
    "Houzé et al. (2020) explain unexpected behaviors by smart home systems.",
    "The xAI literature outlines various objectives for developing xAI methods and systems, with Arrieta et al. (2020) providing a comprehensive overview."
  ]
}